      Constructs an Item with specified properties.
      Parameters:
      name - The name of the item.
      model - The model of the item.
      make - The make of the item.
      date - The date associated with the item.
      value - The value of the item.
      serialNumber - The serial number of the item.
      description - The description of the item.
      comment - Additional comments related to the item.
      tags - The tags associated with the item.
